Comment: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op jp,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}{\blur1}want you here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93698,95867}{\i1}Meimi Haneoka is 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:39.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95867,99162}{\i1}By day she is a happy student\Nat St. Paulia School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99996,103249}{\i1}But at night, she becomes\Nthe phantom thief St. Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:47.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103249,107837}{\i1}to do good deeds for all who come\Nasking for help from Seira, a nun in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:52.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107837,112216}{\i1}Looking to capture the elusive St. Tail\Nis an amateur detective
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112216,115094}{\i1}and Meimi's classmate, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:02:01.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115094,121142}{\i1}As for Meimi, she may have more than\Na bit of interest in such a determined boy.
Comment: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:01.14,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:121142,121142}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122769,127148}Legend of Happiness?\NThe Clock Tower Commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:21.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136366,141579}Did you see the ad for the Wonder Garden?\NIt just opened this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141746,144457}Oh, I love amusement parks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144457,147543}Actually, I've already been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147960,149045}Who with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:31.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150838,151798}If you must know…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154258,156928}Look, it's Tominaga from class C!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156928,158262}Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:43.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159013,163101}It's a wonderful place.\NThe flowers are really lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163101,165728}But the main attraction is… this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167230,169482}The mechanical clock\Nof Wonder Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169482,171526}The dolls move and it's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172235,175738}It was built by a famous\Nforeign doll maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:59.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175738,179659}Every one of his creations\Ncosts a huge amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:06.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180034,186374}Also, they say that if you watch this clock with\Nthe one you love, it'll bring you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186374,188126}And you watched it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188459,189752}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189752,191129}How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191754,195591}I'm jealous, I've never\Neven been on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195967,198302}Who do you want to date, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198302,201556}Don't tell me\Nyou want to date Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202098,203808}Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203808,206394}Who'd want to date\Na dinky detective like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206811,208396}Just who do you think\Nyou're calling "dinky"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:31.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208396,211774}If that bugs you, why don't you go ahead\Nand catch St. Tail, you bungling detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:34.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211774,214861}Even if I do capture her,\NI'm not letting you see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214861,216946}Who cares, she's not like\Nsome beetle on display, is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:37.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216946,217905}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:38.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217905,218990}Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220283,221743}Hey, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222118,223786}Yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:48.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227915,228833}Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233546,234672}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234672,237675}Meimi, there's only one reason\Nwhy I would ask you to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238760,241429}I have a favor to ask of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241971,243931}Something that only she can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244807,246142}The doll at the amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246142,248394}Yes, and it's located\Nin a very high place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248770,250688}You mean that amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250688,253274}Yes, Wonder Garden\NAmusement Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253274,255526}Then, by a high place,\Nyou must mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255526,257987}The mechanical clock\Nof Wonder Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258863,261783}This girl tied a precious doll\Nthat she had brought with her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261783,263951}to the strings of her balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263951,265995}This is the doll you want me to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:32.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265995,272418}Yes, she borrowed the doll from a friend\Nand must return it the next time they meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272794,274003}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288684,290228}The doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:18.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312333,318881}They contacted the amusement park,\Nbut were told to forget about the doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319340,321801}All I have to do is get the doll back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321801,323261}That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323261,325429}Only, you have to get\Nit back by Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325429,327849}Sunday… that's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:33.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328558,333604}The doll's owner is coming to the\Ngirl's house tomorrow to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333604,334689}She needs it by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334689,336440}Which means I have to do it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:40.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336440,340653}And the doll emerges from\Nthe clock on the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340987,343656}So you have to get the doll\Nbefore the balloon carries it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343990,346659}Okay, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349579,350413}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351372,352665}Welcome back, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353374,354750}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354750,355626}This…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356043,357753}You haven't gone\Nthere yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357753,359755}Huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:04.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360214,364468}We were just about to go.\NDo you want to come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367179,369682}It'll complicate things\Nif I go with them…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370016,372351}You want to go, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:12.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372351,372935}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373519,375104}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:19.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375104,379150}Besides, you might find\Nsome ideas for new magic tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380318,382403}Jeez, they always use\Nme as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388159,389619}You want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390536,392788}But I've got work to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393497,395041}Ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395416,396792}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398002,400087}I want you to stay home\Nand watch the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:53.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410181,413476}It's been a long time since I've\Nbeen to an amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414060,415478}It's time for the doll to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416896,418689}Hey, hey… what's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420232,421734}I have something I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428658,429617}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429909,431619}It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435831,436666}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436666,438125}Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438125,440086}What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:23.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440378,443047}To have fun… what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444048,446050}Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446884,449762}So that's the clock tower\Nthe girls were fussing over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455351,458521}When you watch it with the one\Nyou love, it brings happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462984,464986}Why don't they come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466112,467989}Hey there, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468614,469991}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470366,472201}It's just some malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472201,474870}There's a temp repairman here,\Nif I remember correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474870,476956}Yes, I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478708,480543}They say it's just some malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480543,481419}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484630,486966}Ah! My balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488175,489093}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489093,491178}At least I can check\Nif the balloons are still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491762,493764}Too bad, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:18.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493764,498019}I'm going to go get some ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:23.02,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:498019,503024}Employees Only
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511407,513534}Oh, it's a costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520416,522752}Good, it's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528215,529216}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530342,532511}All I did was remove a gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532511,534096}Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534096,535931}The big job's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539518,541062}Identical dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:05.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541062,545483}Why bother with all this stuff?\NWhy not just go ahead and steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545483,547818}The police are on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547818,549570}Sometimes it's better\Nto use your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550488,553449}Well, faking a malfunction and switching\Nthe dolls during the repair,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553449,555534}I guess that's using your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555534,558496}Which means those are all fakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558996,560247}Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563834,566462}Cool it! It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566462,568547}Okay, let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578015,579391}They won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583020,584313}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587274,588859}Please come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:57.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595116,597326}It's an ad for Wonder Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:04.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599120,604166}"I'm going to Wonder Garden\Ntonight to get the doll – St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604166,605251}How dare she!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605251,606669}She was in that rabbit costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614051,616428}I'll return this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616428,617763}Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620307,621517}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621517,623144}That amusement park…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624854,627022}That clock at Wonder Castle…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628691,630067}{\i1}You mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:34.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630526,634488}The one with the dolls that's said to bring\Nhappiness to couples when they view it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634488,635614}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635614,638242}{\i1}Is he trying to ask\Nme to go with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639618,641453}About how much is it worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642580,643455}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643956,646458}Is it true that it's very expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:49.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646458,649003}It's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649003,652464}Why would she do\Nsomething so villainous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655342,657928}I got it, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657928,658888}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661682,664018}{\i1}What's with him, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664351,665686}I hate him!
Comment: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:05.68,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:665686,665686}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:11.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:671692,671692}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:16.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:676697,676697}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682161,684246}He's so insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684830,686999}Oh, look who's grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689168,691712}I'll take you the next time I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693672,695341}I've got to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:37.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696800,697843}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704058,705351}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705351,706352}Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707353,708103}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708812,710022}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710022,711357}She's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:58.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715736,718572}What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721408,723285}I was thinking of going to\Nget some juice or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724453,725704}From the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725704,727831}I thought I'd try something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728832,730668}I'll be off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732127,734964}Going in and out\Nof the window at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734964,737383}She's my girl, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:38.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755067,758737}Please forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:44.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763909,764743}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767121,768414}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770416,772084}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787975,791687}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:34.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810789,814835}That doll was specially made.\NIt's invaluable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814835,817713}There's only one of its\Nkind in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817713,819965}If it were ever stolen…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819965,821633}Please be rest assured…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:45.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821633,825179}St. Tail always has some\Nreason for stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825179,826305}I'm sure it's the same this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826305,828015}You can't be too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:48.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828015,828891}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:54.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828891,834063}If the latest artwork thefts\Nare the work of St. Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834063,835981}then everything falls into place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836690,838484}No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838484,840194}You're still green, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:03.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840194,843322}She may be called "Saint", but\Nshe's no more than a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844615,847451}I'm done with the repairs for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847451,848827}All right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848827,849787}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850329,851038}What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851538,854041}If St. Tail is going to appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854041,856752}it'll be when the dolls come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859421,860631}What the…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.48,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:875479,878482}{\an2}"These dolls are fake!\N– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878857,880359}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880359,881527}When did she…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:44.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881527,884446}Don't tell me she\Nswitched them with fakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886156,887699}St. Tail! Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887699,889993}Stay calm, don't leave your posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891412,894581}They still don't get it?\NTalk about dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900379,902381}I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905300,908053}She's trying to confuse us\Nwith bits of paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908053,910013}I can see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910305,911849}Light her face up! Her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:16.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913350,916895}I can see right through you, too!\NIf you want to light up something,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916895,918897}leave it to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919898,922901}It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924486,926363}The lights are moving\Nby themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946884,948260}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948260,950846}We don't light up at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951180,952848}Now for the real show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959605,961231}Hold it! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:15.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975037,975871}I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999520,1001146}Identical dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001146,1002356}These!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002648,1003941}These are the real ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:47.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003941,1007319}And there's the statue\Nthat was stolen last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007778,1009071}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013033,1014451}You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020415,1022334}Ouch, you're squashing me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038058,1039351}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045691,1048068}The rest of you, go after St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051989,1053282}Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053282,1054199}One…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054199,1055117}Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055117,1056285}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062624,1063917}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063917,1065252}Which one should we arrest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066169,1067754}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069506,1070924}What the…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070924,1074136}Do you have a St. Tail parade\Nor something at this amusement park?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074136,1076263}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082811,1084605}I lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086231,1089735}Fantastic, isn't it?\NSt. Tail's illusion parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:15.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090777,1095490}There's no way to find me in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114426,1115677}{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115927,1117179}Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117179,1119640}No matter where you go…\NI'll find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120265,1121725}{\i1}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123852,1125145}You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127230,1129858}Asuka Jr.! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136448,1137532}Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137532,1139493}I won't…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139868,1141495}miss this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147501,1150087}Like I said… I'm taking\Nthe doll with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150087,1152172}The doll…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152339,1155175}That's the doll you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:19.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155175,1159596}{\i1}If you had asked me out,\Nit would've made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160472,1161098}{\i1}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162641,1164226}It turned out to be\Nlike a date, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164226,1166061}I really enjoyed myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166478,1167854}Date?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168730,1170565}Cut the jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175570,1177364}I'm serious, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186540,1189876}I'm serious… darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191962,1194214}Thank you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:59.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194589,1199010}All of the dolls have been recovered,\Nthanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:04.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199010,1204182}Those two turned out to be the ones\Nresponsible for the art thefts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:08.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204683,1208186}I thought it was strange\Nfor her to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208186,1209062}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209062,1211523}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224494,1227539}Don't ever tie it to a balloon again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237758,1240552}It brings happiness if you watch it\Ntogether with the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241219,1242971}Well, who cares…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:48.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242971,1248393}My nights are always filled\Nwith the prospect of happiness.
