Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:37.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352539,1357544}There is this mister who was swindled out\Nof his painting of cherry Blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357544,1361756}It was a contract under the pretense to borrow it,\Nbut it was a plan to steal it all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:44.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361756,1364634}But a woman from the police force\NRina Takamiya appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:48.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364634,1368805}and gets in the way of my attempts\Nto bring the painting back!
