Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:53.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1371057,1373935}"New Student, Rina!\NA Formidable Enemy".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:57.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1373935,1377272}May the blessings\Nof God be with you.
